title: Jalopnik's Andrew Collins!
description:
Andrew Collins is the chief test driver for Jalopnik who covers it all, from new trucks to fast cars. He's also a passionate off-roader and overlander, how owns  a Scout II as a daily/project 4x4, which is like owning a panther that has both diabetes and narcolepsy. https://andrewpcollins.com/

This podcast is available as a video! https://youtu.be/pQZVC3vuPG4

Follow us!

IG: @thesmokingtire @fakezackklapman @andrewatlarge
